item.dc:creator: @bloodmaniet bloodmaniet
item.description:
@bloodmaniet wrote:

[quote=“Yodoxin, post:2, topic:290152”]To remove the flames search in client.java for:

method58(25106);
method58(25106);

and remove it.

As for the RuneScape icon, search for

 byte abyte0[] = aClass44_1053.method571("title.dat", null);

and remove that.[/quote]
